    JsonItem(oRetVal, "ReceiptDateTime") = C_Str(oFP.GetClock())
    JsonItem(oRetVal, "SerialNo") = oFP.GetSerialNumber()
    JsonItem(oRetVal, "FiscalMemoryNo") = oFP.GetFiscalNumber()
QH:
